意，唇角带着慵懒的笑意。眺望着远处的海平线。\n\n环境： 私人豪华游艇的顶层甲板，以白色为主色调的现代简约风格。甲板铺着昂贵的柚木地板，配以白色的亚麻遮阳伞。周围点缀着新鲜的白玫瑰和白色百合花束。游艇停泊在湛蓝的地中海海域，远眺可见沿岸的悬崖和古堡。远处有私人直升机盘旋。\n\n光线： 地中海炽热的阳光慷慨洒落，游艇甲板明亮耀眼。人物小麦色的肌肤在阳光下泛着健康的光泽。香槟杯折射出璀璨的光芒。海面波光粼粼，反射出无数光点。\n\n拍摄风格： 时尚旅行杂志风格，色调明亮饱和。参考高端度假品牌广告，画面充满奢华与慵懒的气息。整体氛围惬意自在。"],"title":"custom-zit生图"}],"links":[],"version":0.4,"definitions":{"subgraphs":[{"id":"8c926d61-d562-49bc-a2e9-c766aa3b0e5c","version":1,"state":{"lastGroupId":9,"lastNodeId":448,"lastLinkId":668,"lastRerouteId":0},"revision":0,"config":{},"name":"custom-zit生图","inputNode":{"id":-10,"bounding":[-680.9702728892082,249.5901546774874,122.576171875,300]},"outputNode":{"id":-20,"bounding":[1119.8431791916303,287.2317106352529,120,60]},"inputs":[{"id":"415c0d72-b6d8-4680-ada2-0e873478f551","name":"boolean","type":"BOOLEAN","linkIds":[74],"label":"sage加速","pos":[-578.3941010142082,269.59015467748736]},{"id":"07034d35-e433-4d8f-a1ad-9ceab6f015c8","name":"sage_attention","type":"COMBO","linkIds":[75],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,289.59015467748736]},{"id":"6698e09a-5ce9-4cec-acf9-f067b0a07503","name":"width","type":"INT","linkIds":[76],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,309.59015467748736]},{"id":"c9de186d-7132-4d79-a1fd-ea2ccf050c48","name":"height","type":"INT","linkIds":[77],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,329.59015467748736]},{"id":"6d67eddb-77d7-494a-a34e-1142bd16b0b9","name":"batch_size","type":"INT","linkIds":[78],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,349.59015467748736]},{"id":"99ec6ed8-64da-489e-a364-5a58c36a92da","name":"seed","type":"INT","linkIds":[79],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,369.59015467748736]},{"id":"646fd774-d7e9-482a-a37d-ac6059eb685d","name":"steps","type":"INT","linkIds":[80],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,389.59015467748736]},{"id":"72418773-2d13-41a8-b5e9-1bc6d994ab6b","name":"cfg","type":"FLOAT","linkIds":[81],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,409.59015467748736]},{"id":"c0d57b32-efaa-4d59-80fc-cd01abaa4762","name":"sampler_name","type":"COMBO","linkIds":[82],"pos":[-578.3941010142082,429.59015467748736]},{"id":"fe722281-db4